== How to install
- Download the file wss-<version>.xpi
- Drag and Drop onto firefox
- Install the add-on when prompted

== How to use
- Right-click on toolbar > Customize
- Select "Text" or "Icons and Text"
- Drag and Drop "Switch Workspace" button to toolbar
- Now restart firefox
- Click the button or "alt-s" to switch between two workspaces
- Tools > Add-ons > Workspace Switcher > Preferences to change preferences

Notes: -
       1) If the toolbar buttons are displayed as icons only, the
       	  workspace switcher button won't be visible.
       2) Preference change requires restart.
       3) Firefox needs to be restarted after placing button in toolbar.
